### 5. **Register with Google Search Console**

Make your project searchable on Google:

1. Go to: https://search.google.com/search-console/
2. Add property: `https://srinithya1503.github.io/Gen-AI-Projects/smart%20news%20summarizer/`
3. Verify ownership (use HTML tag method)
4. Submit your sitemap
5. Request indexing

### 6. **Create a Screenshot**

Take a nice screenshot of your app and save it as `screenshot.png` in your repository. This makes your README more attractive!

